1. Detects if input is batched (array of images)
2. Uses `prepareImages()` to convert inputs to `RawImage[]`
3. Calls `this.processor(preparedImages)` to get `{ pixel_values }`
4. Manipulates batch dimensions: `batch.dims = [1, ...batch.dims]`
5. Calls `this.model.generate()` with pixel values
