 * text given an image and a text prompt describing what to do with the image.
 *
 * **Example:** Generate a description of an image with `onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft`.
 * ```javascript
 * const generator = await pipeline('image-text-to-text', 'onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft');
